<html>
<head>
     <title>Quiz Page</title>
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="quiz-css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
	
	    <video autoplay loop class="back-video" muted plays-inline>
		    <source src="media/video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
		</video> 	
	    <nav>
		    <img src="media/saturn.png" class="logo">
			<ul class="nav-links">
			    <li><a href="">HOME</a></li>
				<li><a href="">SHOP</a></li>
	            <li><a href="">QUERY FORM</a></li>
				<li><a href="">QUIZ</a></li>
				<li><a href="">SITE MAP</a></li>
				<li><a href="">LATEST</a></li>
				<li><a href="">ABOUT US</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    <div class="start_btn"><button>Start Quiz</button></div>	
    <div class="info_box">
        <div class="info-title"><span>Some Rules of this Quiz</span></div>
        <div class="info-list">
            <div class="info">1. You will have only <span>60 seconds</span> for all the question.</div>
            <div class="info">2. You will have 10 Questions to answer.</div>
            <div class="info">2. Once you select your answer, it can't be undone.</div>
            <div class="info">3. You can't select any option once time goes off.</div>
            <div class="info">4. You can't exit from the Quiz while you're playing.</div>
            <div class="info">5. You'll get points on the basis of your correct answers.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="buttons">
            <button class="quit">Exit Quiz</button>
            <button class="restart">Continue</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz_box">
        <header>
            <div class="title">Quiz Page</div>
            <div class="timer">
                <div class="time_left_txt">Time Left</div>
                <div class="timer_sec">06</div>
            </div>
            <div class="time_line"></div>
        </header>
        <section>
            <div class="que_text">
            </div>
            <div class="option_list">
            </div>
        </section>
        <footer>
            <div class="total_que">
            </div>
            <button class="next_btn">Next Question</button>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <div class="result_box">
        <div class="icon">
            <i class="fas fa-crown"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="complete_text">You've completed the Quiz!</div>
        <div class="score_text"></div>
		<div class="points_taken"></div>
        <div class="buttons">
            <button class="restart">Replay Quiz</button>
            <button class="quit">Quit Quiz</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <canvas id="my-canvas"></canvas>


    <script src="quiz-js/questions.js"></script>


    <script src="quiz-js/script.js"></script>
	    <footer>
			<div class="footer">
				<div class = "container">
					<div class ="row">
						<div class ="footer-col-2">
							<img src ="media/saturn.png" id="footer-logo" alt="logo" class="footer-img">
							<div class="editor">
								<p>Made By <a href="../Abhinav files/editors page.html" id="editor-link">Abhinav Ratnathurai</a></p>
							</div>
							<div class="one-line">
							<p>"Our goal is to consistently make gadgetsÂ beneficial for as many people as possible."</p>
							</div>
						</div> 	
					</div>
					<div>
					<hr>
					<p class ="copyright">Copyright 2022</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>	
</body>
</html>
